LEFT JOIN [People] AS [p] ON [a].[PersonDataId] = [p].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Addresses] AS [a0] ON [p].[AddressId] = [a0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Photos] AS [p0] ON [p].[PhotoId] = [p0].[Id]
